  "title": "",
  "movie": "시크릿 가든 (The Secret Garden)",
  "duration_sec": 744.18,
  "audio_url": "https://rtyzdyyfahddqshgyjvn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/gmp-audio/2020-10-19_screen_english.mp3",
  "artwork_generated_url": "",
  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 14.15,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬"
    },
    {
      "start": 14.15,
      "end": 33.08,
      "text": "Morning Theater"
    },
    {
      "start": 33.08,
      "end": 34.84,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬 타임"
    },
    {
      "start": 34.84,
      "end": 37.02,
      "text": "10월에 함께하고 있는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 37.02,
      "end": 41.74,
      "text": "닉시 엘저릭스, 콜린 퍼스, 줄리 월터즈 주연의"
    },
    {
      "start": 41.74,
      "end": 43.64,
      "text": "The Secret Garden"
    },
    {
      "start": 43.64,
      "end": 46.62,
      "text": "어머 어머 오셨습니다. 이게 누구이십니까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 47.0,
      "end": 47.78,
      "text": "크리스 씨!"
    },
    {
      "start": 48.16,
      "end": 48.56,
      "text": "Hello!"
    },
    {
      "start": 49.18,
      "end": 50.4,
      "text": "It's me. Good morning."
    },
    {
      "start": 50.48,
      "end": 52.38,
      "text": "아주 발랄하게 인사를 한번 드려봤어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 52.44,
      "end": 53.36,
      "text": "Thank you. I like that."
    },
    {
      "start": 53.48,
      "end": 54.6,
      "text": "I like your style."
    },
    {
      "start": 54.74,
      "end": 55.24,
      "text": "감사합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 55.24,
      "end": 58.64,
      "text": "우리 이렇게 따끈따끈한 개봉작인"
    },
    {
      "start": 58.64,
      "end": 60.8,
      "text": "The Secret Garden의 내용을 살펴보고 있는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 60.8,
      "end": 63.14,
      "text": "As we already mentioned,"
    },
    {
      "start": 63.58,
      "end": 66.7,
      "text": "the original novel has been made into movies many times."
    },
    {
      "start": 66.82,
      "end": 67.56,
      "text": "Many movies."
    },
    {
      "start": 67.82,
      "end": 68.06,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 68.14,
      "end": 69.56,
      "text": "Many TV things."
    },
    {
      "start": 69.76,
      "end": 70.54,
      "text": "Yeah, that's right."
    },
    {
      "start": 70.64,
      "end": 72.12,
      "text": "And this movie is one of them."
    },
    {
      "start": 72.4,
      "end": 72.8,
      "text": "그죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 72.96,
      "end": 73.82,
      "text": "This is the latest."
    },
    {
      "start": 74.02,
      "end": 76.16,
      "text": "맞아요. 따끈따끈한 신작이죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 76.32,
      "end": 77.96,
      "text": "And last week, as I remember,"
    },
    {
      "start": 78.16,
      "end": 80.3,
      "text": "we talked about the actor Colin Firth."
    },
    {
      "start": 80.3,
      "end": 82.18,
      "text": "We did talk about Mr. Firth."
    },
    {
      "start": 82.28,
      "end": 82.6,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 82.76,
      "end": 84.42,
      "text": "Who's usually very, very likable."
    },
    {
      "start": 84.58,
      "end": 84.86,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 84.86,
      "end": 86.66,
      "text": "I don't know about in this movie."
    },
    {
      "start": 86.78,
      "end": 87.06,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 87.22,
      "end": 90.1,
      "text": "저도 아직까지는 그렇게 호감형은 아닌 걸로."
    },
    {
      "start": 90.6,
      "end": 92.02,
      "text": "He has a lot of trauma."
    },
    {
      "start": 92.26,
      "end": 92.66,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 93.06,
      "end": 96.16,
      "text": "근데 이 Colin Firth가 이 영화 이전에도"
    },
    {
      "start": 96.16,
      "end": 99.34,
      "text": "비밀의 화원이라는 영화에 출연을 한 적이 있다면서요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.64,
      "end": 100.4,
      "text": "He did."
    },
    {
      "start": 100.54,
      "end": 102.94,
      "text": "He played the same character,"
    },
    {
      "start": 103.88,
      "end": 105.36,
      "text": "Colin Craven."
    },
    {
      "start": 105.78,
      "end": 106.46,
      "text": "그래요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 106.7,
      "end": 107.12,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 107.12,
      "end": 110.54,
      "text": "그 당시에는 이제 Colin의 아버지 역할이 아니라"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.54,
      "end": 112.92,
      "text": "Colin의 역할이었다는 거죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 113.38,
      "end": 114.24,
      "text": "Colin Craven."
    },
    {
      "start": 114.24,
      "end": 114.74,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 114.74,
      "end": 118.28,
      "text": "In a TV movie way back in 1987."
    },
    {
      "start": 119.04,
      "end": 119.32,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 119.4,
      "end": 120.6,
      "text": "The same year I was born."
    },
    {
      "start": 121.48,
      "end": 124.76,
      "text": "So he is, yeah, he is a man of the secret garden."
    },
    {
      "start": 125.04,
      "end": 125.44,
      "text": "아하."
    },
    {
      "start": 126.04,
      "end": 126.28,
      "text": "그래요."
    },
    {
      "start": 126.48,
      "end": 130.14,
      "text": "되게 재밌는 이야기는 또 그 드라마에서는요,"
    },
    {
      "start": 130.22,
      "end": 135.04,
      "text": "주인공들이 다 어른이 된 모습을 보여줬다고 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 135.04,
      "end": 136.28,
      "text": "Yeah, it's a flashback."
    },
    {
      "start": 136.4,
      "end": 136.68,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 136.84,
      "end": 139.34,
      "text": "So in the beginning, Mary is already grown up."
    },
    {
      "start": 139.48,
      "end": 140.66,
      "text": "She's a grown woman."
    },
    {
      "start": 140.66,
      "end": 143.02,
      "text": "And she's remembering her childhood."
    },
    {
      "start": 143.02,
      "end": 143.34,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 143.34,
      "end": 146.14,
      "text": "And she returns to that mansion."
    },
    {
      "start": 146.14,
      "end": 146.82,
      "text": "Uh-huh."
    },
    {
      "start": 146.82,
      "end": 149.1,
      "text": "And she looks for the key to the secret garden."
    },
    {
      "start": 149.1,
      "end": 149.7,
      "text": "Uh-huh."
    },
    {
      "start": 149.7,
      "end": 153.5,
      "text": "And so she's remembering everything that happened way back then."
    },
    {
      "start": 153.5,
      "end": 157.02,
      "text": "Oh, 그게 해피엔딩으로 끝났는지도 좀 궁금한데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 157.02,
      "end": 160.68,
      "text": "Well, it's a little bit of both, happy and sad."
    },
    {
      "start": 161.32,
      "end": 169.94,
      "text": "So Colin, who could not walk for most of the movie, he can walk again at the end, which is a good thing."
    },
    {
      "start": 169.94,
      "end": 176.64,
      "text": "But on the other hand, Dickon, the friend, one of their close friends, is killed in the war."
    },
    {
      "start": 177.18,
      "end": 177.9,
      "text": "What a twist."
    },
    {
      "start": 178.22,
      "end": 178.38,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 178.7,
      "end": 185.94,
      "text": "어, 갑자기 반전인데, 어, Dickon한테는 좀 비극적으로 결말이 지어진 TV 드라마라고 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 186.38,
      "end": 188.8,
      "text": "Anyway, 오늘 장면 먼저 듣고 오겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 189.4,
      "end": 191.68,
      "text": "Nothing's broken, but it looks like it's going rotten."
    },
    {
      "start": 192.81,
      "end": 193.97,
      "text": "There's no running water here."
    },
    {
      "start": 194.69,
      "end": 195.99,
      "text": "That's really good, that."
    },
    {
      "start": 197.06,
      "end": 198.1,
      "text": "It all better, does it, sir?"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.66,
      "end": 198.8,
      "text": "Oh."
    },
    {
      "start": 199.12,
      "end": 200.56,
      "text": "Anything."
    },
    {
      "start": 200.56,
      "end": 201.9,
      "text": "It made it worse."
    },
    {
      "start": 202.0,
      "end": 203.84,
      "text": "Just give it time, both of you."
    },
    {
      "start": 204.34,
      "end": 205.12,
      "text": "We've done all we can."
    },
    {
      "start": 205.4,
      "end": 207.42,
      "text": "We're hoping the garden will magic and well."
    },
    {
      "start": 207.88,
      "end": 209.38,
      "text": "Good morning, we'll have an answer."
    },
    {
      "start": 209.86,
      "end": 213.66,
      "text": "Poor little dog got caught in a bear trap."
    },
    {
      "start": 213.88,
      "end": 215.08,
      "text": "Yeah, he's a cute dog."
    },
    {
      "start": 215.28,
      "end": 216.58,
      "text": "He's not so small."
    },
    {
      "start": 216.86,
      "end": 219.06,
      "text": "He's kind of medium to large size."
    },
    {
      "start": 219.16,
      "end": 219.36,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 219.54,
      "end": 222.2,
      "text": "한 10kg 정도는 되지 않을까 생각이 드는데."
    },
    {
      "start": 222.32,
      "end": 223.04,
      "text": "Curly hair."
    },
    {
      "start": 223.26,
      "end": 223.44,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 223.54,
      "end": 225.16,
      "text": "Brown, like chocolate hair."
    },
    {
      "start": 225.16,
      "end": 225.26,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 225.76,
      "end": 229.88,
      "text": "And 그 trap에 갇혀가지고 결국에는 got hurt 했잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 230.18,
      "end": 230.56,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 230.56,
      "end": 232.78,
      "text": "I guess the wound would be very serious."
    },
    {
      "start": 233.34,
      "end": 233.7,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 234.06,
      "end": 236.34,
      "text": "He's limping every day."
    },
    {
      "start": 236.48,
      "end": 237.64,
      "text": "He can't walk normally."
    },
    {
      "start": 237.98,
      "end": 239.86,
      "text": "And I think it's getting worse and worse."
    },
    {
      "start": 239.98,
      "end": 240.26,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 240.34,
      "end": 242.4,
      "text": "Because nobody is treating his wound."
    },
    {
      "start": 242.5,
      "end": 242.78,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 242.9,
      "end": 244.38,
      "text": "Nobody's tending to his wound."
    },
    {
      "start": 244.5,
      "end": 244.78,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 244.84,
      "end": 249.08,
      "text": "이 다친 강아지가 과연 어떻게 치료를 받을지가 되게 궁금해집니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 249.08,
      "end": 249.52,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 249.64,
      "end": 250.52,
      "text": "Mary needs some help."
    },
    {
      "start": 250.68,
      "end": 250.92,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 250.92,
      "end": 252.88,
      "text": "She doesn't know how to take care of this herself."
    },
    {
      "start": 253.44,
      "end": 255.44,
      "text": "So she goes to find her friend."
    },
    {
      "start": 255.54,
      "end": 256.36,
      "text": "Not friend yet."
    },
    {
      "start": 256.56,
      "end": 257.46,
      "text": "But Dickon."
    },
    {
      "start": 257.58,
      "end": 257.74,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 257.9,
      "end": 258.5,
      "text": "The boy."
    },
    {
      "start": 258.78,
      "end": 260.96,
      "text": "The mysterious boy from the garden."
    },
    {
      "start": 261.18,
      "end": 261.64,
      "text": "Oh."
    },
    {
      "start": 262.0,
      "end": 265.1,
      "text": "I really hope that Dickon has a good idea to treat the dog."
    },
    {
      "start": 265.26,
      "end": 266.56,
      "text": "Let's hope he can heal the dog."
    },
    {
      "start": 266.64,
      "end": 266.94,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 267.3,
      "end": 269.64,
      "text": "자, 어떤 표현이 있었는지 살짝 들여다볼까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 269.64,
      "end": 271.94,
      "text": "It's going rotten."
    },
    {
      "start": 272.26,
      "end": 274.86,
      "text": "아니, 이건 좀 안타까운 이야기 아닙니까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 274.96,
      "end": 275.68,
      "text": "Rotten."
    },
    {
      "start": 275.76,
      "end": 276.04,
      "text": "그죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 276.44,
      "end": 282.08,
      "text": "Rotten이라는 단어는 R-O-T-T-E-N이라고 하는 거니까 썩은이라는 의미잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 282.46,
      "end": 282.72,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 282.86,
      "end": 284.74,
      "text": "상처 부분이 썩기 시작하나 봐요."
    },
    {
      "start": 285.16,
      "end": 285.74,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 286.0,
      "end": 287.36,
      "text": "Usually rotten like food."
    },
    {
      "start": 287.5,
      "end": 290.5,
      "text": "Food is rotten when you leave it out."
    },
    {
      "start": 291.02,
      "end": 293.78,
      "text": "You don't put it in the refrigerator for a few days."
    },
    {
      "start": 293.78,
      "end": 293.98,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 294.56,
      "end": 298.98,
      "text": "But a wound, if a wound is rotten, that means it's infected."
    },
    {
      "start": 299.64,
      "end": 300.88,
      "text": "It's very, very serious."
    },
    {
      "start": 301.08,
      "end": 301.4,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 301.92,
      "end": 302.6,
      "text": "Oh, 그래요."
    },
    {
      "start": 302.72,
      "end": 307.58,
      "text": "강아지의 상처가 it's going rotten이라는 맥락에서 들으실 수 있는 표현이었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 308.02,
      "end": 310.84,
      "text": "썩으려고 해, 썩고 있어 라는 의미겠죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 311.4,
      "end": 312.68,
      "text": "Made it worse."
    },
    {
      "start": 313.08,
      "end": 314.48,
      "text": "Made it worse."
    },
    {
      "start": 314.66,
      "end": 317.46,
      "text": "Worse가 바로 bad의 비교급도 나왔습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 317.58,
      "end": 317.8,
      "text": "그죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 317.88,
      "end": 318.28,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 318.64,
      "end": 322.3,
      "text": "그래서 더 나쁘게 made it 만들었다라는 의미예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 322.3,
      "end": 323.58,
      "text": "You just made it worse."
    },
    {
      "start": 323.8,
      "end": 324.88,
      "text": "Stop it."
    },
    {
      "start": 324.88,
      "end": 326.82,
      "text": "일을 더 나쁘게 만들고 있어."
    },
    {
      "start": 327.14,
      "end": 330.02,
      "text": "좀 그만해 라는 상황에서도 활용할 수 있죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 330.26,
      "end": 331.82,
      "text": "Just give it time."
    },
    {
      "start": 332.24,
      "end": 332.46,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 332.68,
      "end": 333.74,
      "text": "Just give it time."
    },
    {
      "start": 334.1,
      "end": 335.5,
      "text": "시간을 갖고 좀 기다려."
    },
    {
      "start": 335.74,
      "end": 336.7,
      "text": "시간을 두고 봐."
    },
    {
      "start": 336.82,
      "end": 337.86,
      "text": "That's a very good sentence."
    },
    {
      "start": 337.96,
      "end": 338.16,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 338.34,
      "end": 339.74,
      "text": "We use that a whole lot."
    },
    {
      "start": 339.86,
      "end": 340.2,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 340.68,
      "end": 343.48,
      "text": "뭔가 좀, 언제 결과가 나와?"
    },
    {
      "start": 343.94,
      "end": 345.16,
      "text": "빨리 어떻게 좀 해봐?"
    },
    {
      "start": 345.26,
      "end": 346.16,
      "text": "Hey, relax."
    },
    {
      "start": 346.38,
      "end": 346.82,
      "text": "Relax."
    },
    {
      "start": 346.82,
      "end": 350.88,
      "text": "그렇게 닥달하는 사람들에게 이렇게 표현을 해주면 참 좋을 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 350.9,
      "end": 351.08,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 351.22,
      "end": 352.2,
      "text": "Usually for scars."
    },
    {
      "start": 352.44,
      "end": 352.68,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 352.82,
      "end": 356.7,
      "text": "Like you break up with your girlfriend and you cry to your friend."
    },
    {
      "start": 357.14,
      "end": 357.9,
      "text": "Come on, man."
    },
    {
      "start": 357.98,
      "end": 358.5,
      "text": "Relax."
    },
    {
      "start": 358.84,
      "end": 359.82,
      "text": "Just give it time."
    },
    {
      "start": 360.08,
      "end": 361.56,
      "text": "You'll get over it."
    },
    {
      "start": 361.58,
      "end": 362.92,
      "text": "That's a good advice."
    },
    {
      "start": 363.0,
      "end": 364.86,
      "text": "So physical and emotional scars."
    },
    {
      "start": 365.0,
      "end": 365.2,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 365.32,
      "end": 367.62,
      "text": "In this case, the dog has a physical scar."
    },
    {
      "start": 367.7,
      "end": 368.3,
      "text": "That's right."
    },
    {
      "start": 368.68,
      "end": 370.12,
      "text": "자, 이 내용 한 번 더 들어볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 370.12,
      "end": 373.38,
      "text": "Nothing's broken because it looks like it's going rotten."
    },
    {
      "start": 374.47,
      "end": 375.65,
      "text": "There's no running water here."
    },
    {
      "start": 375.65,
      "end": 377.65,
      "text": "That's really good, that."
    },
    {
      "start": 378.58,
      "end": 379.76,
      "text": "I feel better, does it, sir?"
    },
    {
      "start": 380.32,
      "end": 380.46,
      "text": "What?"
    },
    {
      "start": 380.82,
      "end": 382.27,
      "text": "You haven't fixed anything."
    },
    {
      "start": 382.65,
      "end": 383.49,
      "text": "You made it worse."
    },
    {
      "start": 383.63,
      "end": 384.43,
      "text": "Just give it time."
    },
    {
      "start": 384.95,
      "end": 385.49,
      "text": "Both of you."
    },
    {
      "start": 385.99,
      "end": 386.75,
      "text": "We've done all we can."
    },
    {
      "start": 387.07,
      "end": 389.07,
      "text": "We're hoping the garden will magic and well."
    },
    {
      "start": 389.59,
      "end": 390.27,
      "text": "Good morning."
    },
    {
      "start": 390.35,
      "end": 391.01,
      "text": "We'll have an answer."
    },
    {
      "start": 391.57,
      "end": 395.04,
      "text": "Well, happily, Dickon said nothing's broken."
    },
    {
      "start": 395.38,
      "end": 395.56,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 395.82,
      "end": 396.76,
      "text": "That's good news."
    },
    {
      "start": 396.9,
      "end": 397.18,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 397.36,
      "end": 398.42,
      "text": "I'm so glad to hear that."
    },
    {
      "start": 398.42,
      "end": 402.64,
      "text": "Sometimes, you know, when you fall down or someone close to you falls down."
    },
    {
      "start": 402.94,
      "end": 404.06,
      "text": "Oh, is anything broken?"
    },
    {
      "start": 404.26,
      "end": 404.62,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 404.78,
      "end": 405.74,
      "text": "어디 부러진 데는 없어?"
    },
    {
      "start": 405.84,
      "end": 406.54,
      "text": "You get worried."
    },
    {
      "start": 406.54,
      "end": 407.08,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 407.26,
      "end": 409.08,
      "text": "But nothing's broken in this case."
    },
    {
      "start": 409.3,
      "end": 411.66,
      "text": "네, 다행히 상처가 났을 뿐."
    },
    {
      "start": 411.92,
      "end": 413.24,
      "text": "뭐 썩고 있다고는 했겠지만."
    },
    {
      "start": 413.56,
      "end": 414.72,
      "text": "That's the bad part."
    },
    {
      "start": 414.8,
      "end": 415.24,
      "text": "그래요."
    },
    {
      "start": 415.4,
      "end": 416.32,
      "text": "뭐가 좋은지 모르겄네."
    },
    {
      "start": 416.4,
      "end": 417.14,
      "text": "썩고 있다고."
    },
    {
      "start": 417.44,
      "end": 419.3,
      "text": "네, 첫 번째 문자부터 시작할까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 420.08,
      "end": 423.96,
      "text": "Nothing's broken, but it looks like it's going rotten."
    },
    {
      "start": 424.54,
      "end": 425.76,
      "text": "Nothing's broken."
    },
    {
      "start": 426.3,
      "end": 427.38,
      "text": "부러진 데는 없어."
    },
    {
      "start": 427.38,
      "end": 430.36,
      "text": "But it looks like it's going rotten."
    },
    {
      "start": 430.36,
      "end": 434.46,
      "text": "그런데 상처가 지금 썩으려고 하고 있어라는 말입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 434.92,
      "end": 435.36,
      "text": "Uh-oh."
    },
    {
      "start": 435.42,
      "end": 435.88,
      "text": "Uh-oh."
    },
    {
      "start": 436.32,
      "end": 438.52,
      "text": "We need to treat that wound ASAP."
    },
    {
      "start": 438.8,
      "end": 439.16,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 439.82,
      "end": 441.62,
      "text": "Is there running water here?"
    },
    {
      "start": 441.78,
      "end": 443.34,
      "text": "갑자기 왜 물을 찾는 거지?"
    },
    {
      "start": 443.58,
      "end": 443.98,
      "text": "Water."
    },
    {
      "start": 443.98,
      "end": 446.44,
      "text": "네, 물로 씻어주기만 한다는 이야기일까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 446.6,
      "end": 447.82,
      "text": "We need to wash the wound."
    },
    {
      "start": 448.16,
      "end": 449.08,
      "text": "네, 그렇긴 한데."
    },
    {
      "start": 449.2,
      "end": 450.52,
      "text": "Is there running water here?"
    },
    {
      "start": 450.94,
      "end": 452.8,
      "text": "여기 흐르는 물이 근처에 없나?"
    },
    {
      "start": 453.02,
      "end": 454.1,
      "text": "라고 질문을 하고 있어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 454.24,
      "end": 455.8,
      "text": "Still water is dirty."
    },
    {
      "start": 456.16,
      "end": 459.28,
      "text": "Running water is supposed to be relatively clean."
    },
    {
      "start": 459.44,
      "end": 460.18,
      "text": "네, 그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 460.28,
      "end": 461.64,
      "text": "흐르는 물이 좀 중요합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 461.64,
      "end": 464.51,
      "text": "That's really good, that."
    },
    {
      "start": 465.35,
      "end": 467.01,
      "text": "Feel better, does it, sir?"
    },
    {
      "start": 467.77,
      "end": 468.01,
      "text": "Up?"
    },
    {
      "start": 468.37,
      "end": 472.01,
      "text": "네, 지금 딕건이 계속 이야기하고 있는 문장들이잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 472.03,
      "end": 473.35,
      "text": "Is he talking to the dog?"
    },
    {
      "start": 473.47,
      "end": 474.57,
      "text": "Yeah, I think so too."
    },
    {
      "start": 474.59,
      "end": 476.43,
      "text": "Sir, he's very respectful."
    },
    {
      "start": 476.73,
      "end": 477.07,
      "text": "그러게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 477.19,
      "end": 482.13,
      "text": "이 강아지한테도 sir 이런 존칭을 활용했다는 게 되게 재미있는 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 482.23,
      "end": 483.47,
      "text": "Very polite young gentleman."
    },
    {
      "start": 484.47,
      "end": 486.25,
      "text": "뭐라고 하는지 해석을 해드리면"
    },
    {
      "start": 486.25,
      "end": 487.31,
      "text": "That's really good."
    },
    {
      "start": 487.81,
      "end": 489.01,
      "text": "Yeah, 이거 아주 좋은데."
    },
    {
      "start": 489.33,
      "end": 489.61,
      "text": "That."
    },
    {
      "start": 489.95,
      "end": 491.49,
      "text": "Feel better, does it, sir?"
    },
    {
      "start": 491.83,
      "end": 493.67,
      "text": "좀 기분이 나아지지 않았어?"
    },
    {
      "start": 493.83,
      "end": 495.43,
      "text": "좀 상태가 훨씬 나아졌지?"
    },
    {
      "start": 496.01,
      "end": 497.01,
      "text": "그 다음에 up!"
    },
    {
      "start": 497.09,
      "end": 497.33,
      "text": "Up!"
    },
    {
      "start": 497.57,
      "end": 497.97,
      "text": "일어나!"
    },
    {
      "start": 498.21,
      "end": 498.71,
      "text": "라고 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 499.01,
      "end": 499.41,
      "text": "Sir?"
    },
    {
      "start": 499.49,
      "end": 501.65,
      "text": "이라고 해놓고서 갑자기 명령문으로 up!"
    },
    {
      "start": 501.79,
      "end": 502.45,
      "text": "하고 있어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 503.01,
      "end": 504.23,
      "text": "앞뒤 좋았나네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 504.29,
      "end": 504.89,
      "text": "그러게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 505.03,
      "end": 506.27,
      "text": "Sir, up!"
    },
    {
      "start": 506.57,
      "end": 506.83,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 507.25,
      "end": 509.33,
      "text": "Please, can you try to stand up, sir?"
    },
    {
      "start": 511.61,
      "end": 514.55,
      "text": "Dickon, you haven't fixed anything."
    },
    {
      "start": 515.13,
      "end": 516.45,
      "text": "제가 하고 싶은 말이었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 516.45,
      "end": 521.29,
      "text": "흐르는 물에다가 그 강아지의 상처를 살짝 씻어주기만 했을 뿐이잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 521.83,
      "end": 525.11,
      "text": "Dickon, Dickon, you haven't fixed anything."
    },
    {
      "start": 525.57,
      "end": 527.39,
      "text": "너는 어떤 것도 고친 게 없어."
    },
    {
      "start": 527.89,
      "end": 529.81,
      "text": "Hey, he bandaged it up."
    },
    {
      "start": 529.89,
      "end": 532.11,
      "text": "He wrapped it up with some gauze."
    },
    {
      "start": 532.11,
      "end": 532.81,
      "text": "Very simple."
    },
    {
      "start": 533.21,
      "end": 534.53,
      "text": "Come on, give it some time."
    },
    {
      "start": 534.59,
      "end": 535.77,
      "text": "Give it some time, Mary."
    },
    {
      "start": 535.97,
      "end": 537.11,
      "text": "Have some patience."
    },
    {
      "start": 537.11,
      "end": 540.25,
      "text": "But she doesn't have patience right now."
    },
    {
      "start": 540.47,
      "end": 542.95,
      "text": "She wants it solved right away."
    },
    {
      "start": 543.07,
      "end": 543.53,
      "text": "그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 544.05,
      "end": 545.37,
      "text": "You've made it worse."
    },
    {
      "start": 545.53,
      "end": 547.11,
      "text": "네, 이 문장 미리 들어보셨잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 548.09,
      "end": 549.47,
      "text": "You've made it worse."
    },
    {
      "start": 549.97,
      "end": 552.35,
      "text": "너는 상황을 더 나쁘게 만들었잖아."
    },
    {
      "start": 552.67,
      "end": 554.41,
      "text": "라고 신경질적으로 이야기를 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 554.67,
      "end": 558.43,
      "text": "Yeah, so the dog is still limping, still whining, in pain."
    },
    {
      "start": 558.43,
      "end": 560.79,
      "text": "And so Mary is a little frustrated."
    },
    {
      "start": 561.01,
      "end": 561.31,
      "text": "그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 561.37,
      "end": 562.11,
      "text": "저도 이해가 됩니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 563.15,
      "end": 565.89,
      "text": "Just give it time, both of you."
    },
    {
      "start": 565.95,
      "end": 567.65,
      "text": "지금 약간 take it easy."
    },
    {
      "start": 567.85,
      "end": 570.07,
      "text": "이렇게 약간 완화를 시켜주고자 하는 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 570.41,
      "end": 571.55,
      "text": "Just give it time."
    },
    {
      "start": 571.93,
      "end": 572.93,
      "text": "아, 좀 기다려봐."
    },
    {
      "start": 573.29,
      "end": 574.65,
      "text": "시간을 좀 줘봐."
    },
    {
      "start": 575.09,
      "end": 575.91,
      "text": "Both of you."
    },
    {
      "start": 576.13,
      "end": 577.69,
      "text": "너랑 강아지 둘다 말이야."
    },
    {
      "start": 577.85,
      "end": 578.67,
      "text": "라는 의도겠죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 578.67,
      "end": 581.13,
      "text": "Yeah, it can't get better right away."
    },
    {
      "start": 581.21,
      "end": 581.57,
      "text": "그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 581.61,
      "end": 582.55,
      "text": "Like a miracle."
    },
    {
      "start": 582.81,
      "end": 584.71,
      "text": "We need to give it some time."
    },
    {
      "start": 585.85,
      "end": 587.41,
      "text": "We've done all we can."
    },
    {
      "start": 587.55,
      "end": 589.75,
      "text": "Yeah, we've done all we can."
    },
    {
      "start": 590.21,
      "end": 591.85,
      "text": "우리가 할 수 있는 것은 다 했어."
    },
    {
      "start": 592.11,
      "end": 592.57,
      "text": "라는 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 593.09,
      "end": 596.67,
      "text": "물로 씻어주고 이렇게 붐대를 감아주는 정도."
    },
    {
      "start": 597.13,
      "end": 599.53,
      "text": "이게 우리가 할 수 있는 모든 걸 다 했다는 이야기인가요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 599.81,
      "end": 601.59,
      "text": "Yeah, there's no vet nearby."
    },
    {
      "start": 601.91,
      "end": 603.73,
      "text": "We can't take this dog to a vet."
    },
    {
      "start": 603.93,
      "end": 604.79,
      "text": "그렇긴 한데."
    },
    {
      "start": 604.89,
      "end": 606.35,
      "text": "We've done everything we can."
    },
    {
      "start": 606.35,
      "end": 608.29,
      "text": "아직까지는 뭔가 설득력이 없어 보이는 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 608.67,
      "end": 609.55,
      "text": "뭐 그럴 수 있지만."
    },
    {
      "start": 609.59,
      "end": 609.75,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 610.35,
      "end": 611.63,
      "text": "뭐, 어린 아이들이에요."
    },
    {
      "start": 611.69,
      "end": 611.87,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 612.61,
      "end": 613.83,
      "text": "이거 하는 게 대단해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 613.95,
      "end": 614.19,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 615.53,
      "end": 618.79,
      "text": "We're hoping the garden will magic him well."
    },
    {
      "start": 619.19,
      "end": 620.55,
      "text": "오, we're hoping."
    },
    {
      "start": 620.73,
      "end": 622.11,
      "text": "우리는 바랄 뿐이래요."
    },
    {
      "start": 622.21,
      "end": 624.75,
      "text": "The garden will magic him well."
    },
    {
      "start": 625.31,
      "end": 628.91,
      "text": "이 문장에서 그러니까 magic을 약간 verb처럼 사용을 한 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 629.07,
      "end": 630.71,
      "text": "A very, very special usage."
    },
    {
      "start": 630.73,
      "end": 630.97,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 631.15,
      "end": 632.93,
      "text": "It's not usually used like this."
    },
    {
      "start": 632.93,
      "end": 633.17,
      "text": "맞아요, 맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 633.17,
      "end": 636.09,
      "text": "이게 명사로는 우리가 많이 들어봤잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 636.19,
      "end": 637.09,
      "text": "magic, 마법."
    },
    {
      "start": 637.09,
      "end": 642.19,
      "text": "근데 동사로는 거의 쓰이는 경우는 드문 것 같은데 여기에서는 동사로 쓰였어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 642.25,
      "end": 642.99,
      "text": "Very 특이해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 643.13,
      "end": 644.41,
      "text": "Yeah, very 특이해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 645.09,
      "end": 645.79,
      "text": "Very special."
    },
    {
      "start": 646.01,
      "end": 655.15,
      "text": "네, 정원이 will magic him well 이라고 했으니까 마법을 그에게 잘 부려주기를 we're helping, 바라는 수밖에."
    },
    {
      "start": 655.59,
      "end": 657.07,
      "text": "이렇게 해석하시면 좋을 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 657.07,
      "end": 658.79,
      "text": "The garden will heal him."
    },
    {
      "start": 658.93,
      "end": 659.69,
      "text": "That's right."
    },
    {
      "start": 659.79,
      "end": 661.79,
      "text": "It is a magic garden, after all."
    },
    {
      "start": 661.85,
      "end": 662.13,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 662.23,
      "end": 663.47,
      "text": "You don't know what will happen."
    },
    {
      "start": 664.98,
      "end": 667.34,
